quran[15]{c,v,t,f}:
  26,145,"Èmi kò sì bèèrè owó-ọ̀yà kan ní ọwọ́ yín lórí rẹ̀. Kò sí ẹ̀san mi lọ́dọ̀ ẹnì kan àfi lọ́dọ̀ Olúwa gbogbo ẹ̀dá."
  26,146,"Ṣé kí wọ́n fi yín sílẹ̀ síbi n̄ǹkan tí ó wà (nílé ayé) níbí yìí (nínú ìgbádùn ayé, kí ẹ jẹ́) olùfọkànbalẹ̀"
  26,147,"nínú àwọn ọgbà oko àti ìṣẹ́lẹ̀rú omi."
  29,58,"Àwọn tó gbàgbọ́ ní òdodo, tí wọ́n sì ṣe àwọn iṣẹ́ rere, dájúdájú A máa fi wọn sínú àwọn ilé pẹ̀tẹ́ẹ̀sì gígá kan nínú Ọgbà Ìdẹ̀ra, tí odò ń ṣàn ní ìsàlẹ̀ rẹ̀. Olùṣegbére ni wọ́n nínú rẹ̀. Ẹ̀san àwọn olùṣe-rere sì dára."
  29,59,"(Àwọn ni) àwọn tó ṣe sùúrù. Olúwa wọn sì ni wọ́n ń gbáralé."
  29,60,"Mélòó mélòó nínú àwọn ẹranko tí kò lè dá bùkátà ìjẹ-ìmu rẹ̀ gbé, tí Allāhu sì ń ṣe ìjẹ-ìmu fún àwọn àti ẹ̀yin. Òun sì ni Olùgbọ́, Onímọ̀."
  30,37,"Ṣé wọn kò wòye pé dájúdájú Allāhu l’Ó ń tẹ́ ọrọ̀ sílẹ̀ fún ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́, (Ó sì ń) díwọ̀n rẹ̀ (fún ẹni tí Ó bá fẹ́)? Dájúdájú àwọn àmì wà nínú ìyẹn fún ìjọ tó gbàgbọ́."
  30,38,"Nítorí náà, fún ẹbí ni ẹ̀tọ́ rẹ̀. (Fún) mẹ̀kúnnù àti onírìn-àjò (tí agara dá ní n̄ǹkan). Ìyẹn lóore jùlọ fún àwọn tó ń fẹ́ Ojú rere Allāhu. Àwọn wọ̀nyẹn, àwọn sì ni olùjèrè."
  30,39,"Ohunkóhun tí ẹ bá fún (àwọn ènìyàn) ní ẹ̀yáwó, nítorí kí ó lè di èlé láti ara dúkìá àwọn ènìyàn, kò lè lékún ní ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu. Ohunkóhun tí ẹ bá sì (fún àwọn ènìyàn) ní Zakāh, tí ẹ̀ ń fẹ́ ojú rere Allāhu, àwọn wọ̀nyẹn ni A máa fún ní àdìpèlé ẹ̀san."
  31,22,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá jura rẹ̀ sílẹ̀ fún Allāhu, tí ó jẹ́ olùṣe-rere, dájúdájú onítọ̀un ti dìrọ̀ mọ́ okùn tó fọkàn balẹ̀ jùlọ. Àti pé ọ̀dọ̀ Allāhu ni ìkángun àwọn ọ̀rọ̀ (ẹ̀dá) wà."
  31,23,"Ẹnikẹ́ni tí ó bá sì ṣàì gbàgbọ́, má ṣe jẹ́ kí àìgbàgbọ́ rẹ̀ kó ìbànújẹ́ bá ọ. Ọ̀dọ̀ Wa ni ibùpadàsí wọn. Nígbà náà, A máa fún wọn ní ìró ohun tí wọ́n ṣe níṣẹ́. Dájúdájú Allāhu ni Onímọ̀ nípa ohun tí ń bẹ nínú igbá-àyà ẹ̀dá."
  31,24,"A máa fún wọn ní ìgbádùn díẹ̀. Lẹ́yìn náà, A máa taari wọn sínú ìyà tó nípọn."
  32,7,"Ẹni tó ṣe gbogbo n̄ǹkan tí Ó ṣẹ̀dá rẹ̀ ní dáadáa. Ó sì bẹ̀rẹ̀ ìṣẹ̀dá ènìyàn láti inú ẹrẹ̀."
  32,8,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó ṣe àwọn àrọ́mọdọ́mọ rẹ̀ láti ara ohun tí A mú jáde láti ara omi lílẹ yẹpẹrẹ."
  32,9,"Lẹ́yìn náà, Ó to (oríkèéríkèé) rẹ̀ dọ́gba. Ó sì fẹ́ (ẹ̀mí) sí i lára nínú ẹ̀mí Rẹ̀ (tí Ó dá).Ó tún ṣe ìgbọ́rọ̀, ìríran àti ọkàn fún yín. Díẹ̀ ni ọpẹ́ tí ẹ̀ ń dá! {1}",footnotes:1:[“ẹ̀mí” nínú āyah yìí ṣe wẹ́kú “ẹ̀mí” tó jẹyọ nínú sūrah an-Nisā’;  4:171.]
